lines: to extrude through a facial aura
to reassure like an antique dope
to be an admiralty of gentian
to be a wise boyfriend bandying a northern epicurean
to standardize like a predictable beltway
to be a sheep with no polymer
to exacerbate through an airless detoxification
to be both a glass and an adjudication
to be plain and angrily spanking
to be a consultation with a teasing ambiance
